---
title: Premium Steak Fillet & Hasselback Potato Feast with Mediterranean-Roasted Eggplant & Herby Mayo
description: A juicy tender steak is one thing, but the right condiment takes it to the next level of deliciousness. We've added a bright parsley-garlic sauce and a side of Argentinian-style roasted carrot to give the classic steak and three veg a flavourful and worldly upgrade.
